TITLE: Episode 68 - Boobs and Freedom with @TweetsByBritt
DESCRIPTION: This week, Maddie and I sit down with Britt for the illustrious “The Freckles and Britt Show”. We talk COVID, lockdowns, elections, vaccinations, what it’s like living and being high risk within the current paradigm, being a liberty lady on social media and, of course, boobs.
